;+
; NAME:
;       FACTOR
; PURPOSE:
;       Find prime factors of a given number.
; CATEGORY:
; CALLING SEQUENCE:
;       factor, x, p, n
; INPUTS:
;       x = Number to factor.            in
; KEYWORD PARAMETERS:
; OUTPUTS:
;       p = Array of prime numbers.      out
;       n = Count of each element of p.  out
; COMMON BLOCKS:
; NOTES:
;       Note: see also prime, numfactors, print_fact.
; MODIFICATION HISTORY:
;       R. Sterner.  4 Oct, 1988.
